          "reviewBody": "The school has the most experienced and best teachers in town. But they're more inclined towards studies than ECA. Moreover, ECA is now increasingly being outsourced via tie-ups and being charged extra for by the school. Deliver of subjects like Maths and Science is very reformed and practical, while computers and foreign language remain the opposite.",
