            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Everything is good. However, I strongly believe that they should install Ac in all the classrooms. With scorching summer heat, kids can hardly focus on their studies in the classroom. By the time they come home they are already exhausted. One should see the faces of the students at the time of dispersal...sweaty, tired and red. I don't know what is taking them so long to do this.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
