            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is the worst school on the history and future of any schools. Along with gender discrimination, they also promote traumatising of children through teachers. They want the fee on time but won’t address the parents issue if there are any. Bullying is very common here among students. My younger sister had to face a lot while being in this school & id request anyone who’s reading this to get your child admitted in ANY school but NOT DPS (any branch) because they’re all the same. Thanks",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
