          "reviewBody": "The school is okay okay, don’t expect as perfect school. Transportation is pathetic, they are providing local Bus for kids, which is not safe and not providing AC facility even after huge fee increase.\n\nkids are having problem in summers.\nSchool notifications are never on time. just okay school like any other school in greater noida.",
          "publisher": {
