          "reviewBody": "Excellent premises, neat and clean, first time visited this school with my granddaughter who  taken admission in St One this year, Class teacher is superb in all respect, explained all activities n module of teaching in a very good manner, very courteous.Met Headmistress madam also,who is courteous beyond expectations.Personally came till chamber door while I was coming back.Her behaviour was wonderful.I am happy that I shifted my granddaughter to this school from another so-called reputed school of Greater Noida .",
